Generate_branched_alkane¶

conformer_rl.molecule_generation.generation.generate_branched_alkane.generate_branched_alkane(num_atoms: int, save: bool = False) → rdkit.Chem.rdchem.Mol¶

Generates a branched alkane.

Parameters

  • num_atoms (int) – Number of atoms in molecule to be generated.

  • save (bool) – Whether to save the molecule as a .mol file.
